{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "e7819da8-6429-40a8-8f8d-fe9540ebdb49",
    "name": "Magic Class Session 2 08 - Moral Magic",
    "sceneId": "981d126b-abc7-430a-abb4-e912340c59e6",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "4e2d098c-25b2-48a4-b63a-29f3f9b96c2a",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "e6c5e309-2f24-4d7b-99fc-75444f1913bf",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "4d08a6ba-156e-4d70-8048-9c6dc04728b8",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "For this lesson, we are going to take the time to discuss the moral ramifications of magic and its usage. Since you all strive to become heroes, it behooves you to consider the consequences of your actions.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "f04eed21-767e-4dc2-afb3-3afbc5dfa609",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "In the course of this class, you have learned how to create some useful magical tools and spells. These are the means by which you forge your own future and that of the people around you.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "18dddcdd-21b9-4d4a-97ae-186a8e0799db",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Your magic is merely a tool. It can be used for good or for ill. Is it for the good of others that you explore dangerous places like the Sea Caves - or merely for your own personal gain?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "6d3f250c-1f6b-4013-a624-9fc6757903b6",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Exploration and adventuring are dangerous activities that can have disastrous outcomes. Killing sentient creatures like Gogs might well cause a war with them. Opening a sealed gateway may release something terrible into this world.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "fa2dbe63-eca3-4490-a2ea-67858a881a90",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "I have given you tools... It is your duty to use them wisely.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "7545a114-ef19-4441-9021-9bc28fb1bde1",
                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                    "text": "Does anyone have a suggestion on how to best use your magic for the good of others?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "84df4608-b4bc-4a9f-b0f5-a37d72c1acfd",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "0002db13-9c01-4c82-b58f-ec7dfdc1579c",
                            "text": "Talk About Rescuing Joel",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d88e1a5c-e7ef-4c42-9e51-6ff87be2e7c3",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "When my classmate, Joel Kyro, was missing in the Catacombs, I had to use a lot of the runestones and magic just to stay alive long enough to find my friend.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "01d3a96f-b14f-46c5-9fab-31e57973c1f7",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "The Catacombs can be incredibly dangerous, particularly so at this time a year. I am so tickled that you put your magic to such a heroic cause as in rescuing a lost comrade.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "e06fbd68-58db-4ac7-b98c-08e43f15a743",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "id": "92998d21-a632-4121-90c0-8a5b2358298a",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "70",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                "scope": "actor",
                                "scopeId": "4b05c425-ca25-4abb-9a36-7d793370842f",
                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                "tags": "KyroSaved",
                                "has": true
                            },
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "c7cf940e-70d5-4d4e-a381-0001a972bc4e",
                            "text": "Talk About Gogs and Zombies",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ac24195b-801d-40bb-8b88-36b87bbc87a3",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "In the Sea Caves, I had to use my runestones to get past the Gogs and Zombies, and my Sense Magic to find hidden magic.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "477b9794-6f16-4a53-a58c-c47693ca2ae7",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "I am pleased that you put your knowledge of magic to use, but why were you in the Sea Caves in the first place? It's an unpleasantly dangerous place to be.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "573eac34-941b-4598-8521-a7fc65c310d4",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "faf75a1f-d319-462c-8031-baa9b117b0cb",
                                            "text": "Say You Were Saving a Friend",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "6a016925-a18f-4c13-884e-cdb8eb41cfc7",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "text": "I learned that a dear friend was searching the Sea Caves for a way to prove her worth to her father. I could not let her face such dangers alone and I did what I could to keep her safe.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "b3768d10-3d69-4dd8-8f27-d8104723f4f1",
                                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "How very noble of you to help your friend with her goal. It is so good to know that mundane Magic Users such as yourself can use magic heroically.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "id": "eecdc37e-3e7f-4ae4-987a-9cdaf0134c54",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                                    "target": "70",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "9a3e3067-afd0-439c-a2ae-e9833f76041a",
                                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "amount": "2",
                                                    "change": "1",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "4",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "a5b72c87-e5d9-4186-b2a5-d1ba2c97eec3",
                                            "text": "Say You Were Defeating an Ancient Evil",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "af29a1f2-4184-484f-b0d0-6c8d6fbfd5ad",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "text": "I heard rumors that there was an unspeakable horror lurking in the dark depths of the Sea Caves. Somebody had to defeat the creature before it attacked Caligari's sea port.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "1d703c93-006c-4aa3-a966-e7d9a768f0df",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "text": "Who better than I? I had the skills, the magic, and the cleverness to send that horror back to the depths of the sea.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "ef333294-005c-4eaa-aa1b-f305d6c16421",
                                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "How astonishing!",
                                                    "emotion": "4",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "id": "b51c971c-bbcb-4b1c-9eeb-28646be88fac",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                                    "target": "70",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "7319c396-b230-447a-9574-3632474f8094",
                                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                                "amount": "2",
                                                                "change": "1",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "4d3e8a71-cb9b-40f2-95d0-b8333aae6daf",
                                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                                "amount": "2",
                                                                "change": "0",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "4",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "6c7de920-b5b3-444c-8535-f03ce19edca0",
                                            "text": "Say You Were Saving a Trapped Creature",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "2ac051d1-59d7-4c2c-ac2c-9845208c529f",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "text": "I was exploring the Sea Caves for a friend, doing my best to avoid combat and other dangers there. However, I discovered a large Sea Serpent had been trapped by the Gogs.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "f46d36b3-4faa-486c-9994-dd54da4f656f",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "text": "I befriended the monster by feeding it and then set it free to so that it could swim out to sea.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "42ba2e86-04e2-42fb-85c8-e764b5d6eeda",
                                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "That was very honorable of you - particularly the part about exploring the Sea Caves for a friend.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "id": "73e271c9-8e55-4cbb-9f32-e7dca5f27cd3",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                                    "target": "70",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "24e15f59-725c-42e7-9b18-8ea9e6aebbb1",
                                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "amount": "2",
                                                    "change": "1",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "5",
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "b4ca31e1-b0c1-40d7-9581-6d91f9f5d4ce",
                                            "text": "Say You Were Trying to Get Rich to Help Your Mother",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "373d7c11-bb5c-49ec-9f35-c6f1daeb0e73",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "text": "I was searching the Sea Caves for treasure in order to buy a home and a piano for my mother so that she didn't have to work her fingers to the bone cleaning other people's houses.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "4b975081-e921-48d0-a991-e4193c1a16e9",
                                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "It's very sweet of you to risk your life to help your mother. I am sure that she must be very proud of you right now.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0"
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "id": "130c5c7d-5ce3-4810-83a2-e79c8a6bcc03",
                                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                                    "target": "70",
                                                    "success": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": [
                                                            {
                                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                                "id": "45e50196-10eb-4b6a-9db5-b02a93eec72f",
                                                                "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                                                "amount": "2",
                                                                "change": "1",
                                                                "notify": true
                                                            }
                                                        ]
                                                    },
                                                    "failure": {
                                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                                        "nodes": []
                                                    },
                                                    "notify": true
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": 0,
                                            "ExitMenu": false
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                                    "Unique": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": {
                                "type": "expressions.inTags",
                                "scope": "actor",
                                "scopeId": "0b49e2c8-5b7f-4534-bd10-21a0a36a6cbe",
                                "scopeFilterId": null,
                                "tags": "TreasureOnHerOwn",
                                "has": false
                            },
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "664dd998-80bc-4ad0-be9b-6527550a2afa",
                            "text": "Suggest Protecting the Castle From Undead",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "62e042e2-8f7d-425d-a05d-0a2ad58ecf6c",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "text": "Well, when the Nights of the Dead occur, we can use our Claustra runestones and Null runestones to protect non-Magic Users from Ghosties and Ghoulies and Long-Legged Beasties.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7bd7c84a-f898-4165-a729-0fdd98790882",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It's a noble thought, but this castle is well-protected against hostile Undead. Any Ghosts you see within the castle walls will not deliberately harm people.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0cbaf53e-88f3-4596-aad6-a4b764ef7db4",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "However, even benevolent spirits can inadvertently feed upon your life energy. Ghosts are best to be avoided by the living.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                    "id": "63007144-a9f3-4424-b678-b39b3b44fc29",
                                    "actorId": "59d4db68-0e1f-4cca-8118-eb49edcf3859",
                                    "amount": "2",
                                    "change": "1",
                                    "notify": true
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "7a96116c-1d54-4219-a61d-43c3d4ec8a54",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": false
                        }
                    ],
                    "AutoAddDone": false,
                    "Unique": true
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "5b0976c0-9a42-49b6-9533-2f9adfec5d42",
